citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at approximately
12:10 pm on 12/14/2015.
The inspector knocked on the door, honked the horn, called the database phone number and left a message, called
the cell phone number (busy signal), waited thirty minutes, called the cell phone number again (busy signal), and
then left the facility. No contact was made with the licensee.
